1
00:01:39,519 --> 00:01:40,920
How did you get so badly hurt?

2
00:01:56,079 --> 00:01:57,439
On a night like this

3
00:01:58,760 --> 00:01:59,599
why would your family

4
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,640
send a young lady like you

5
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:02,480
out here all alone?

6
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:10,520
My mother is ill.

7
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:12,360
My father

8
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,280
is tied up at the yamen.

9
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:17,120
He can't get away.

10
00:02:20,439 --> 00:02:21,960
Leaving the search to the servants—

11
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,000
for one thing

12
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,199
I worry they might not

13
00:02:24,199 --> 00:02:25,360
recognize Rong.

14
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,439
And also I'm worried

15
00:02:28,199 --> 00:02:29,400
that if anything changes

16
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,240
I can make a decision right away.

17
00:03:13,479 --> 00:03:14,879
Your wound has been cleaned.

18
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:16,639
Now

19
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,039
I'll apply the medicine.

20
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:19,879
Alright.

21
00:04:58,800 --> 00:04:59,800
Rong, are you alright?

22
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:00,720
Thank goodness you're back!
You're safe now.

23
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,040
Miss Gu was worried sick.
We were all so worried.

24
00:05:03,079 --> 00:05:04,040
We were frantic.

25
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,439
That was so dangerous, don't you think?

26
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:08,519
How is he?
You're fine? No one's hurt, right?

27
00:05:09,319 --> 00:05:09,879
How is everything?

28
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,120
You've been through a lot.
I'm fine.

29
00:05:14,519 --> 00:05:15,319
Rong.

30
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,560
Jinzhao.

31
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,199
Keep sending people to search.

32
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:20,959
Jinzhao
I...

33
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,079
How did you end up like this?

34
00:05:25,839 --> 00:05:26,759
What are you doing here?

35
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,360
Lord Chen's guards

36
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:29,920
found me.

37
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:32,600
He sent them out
last night.

38
00:05:33,759 --> 00:05:35,360
And they actually tracked Rong down

39
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,480
in a village miles away.

40
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,560
Lord Chen's men are truly capable.

41
00:05:38,879 --> 00:05:39,879
We searched for ages

42
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:41,120
and got nowhere.

43
00:05:41,759 --> 00:05:42,800
What matters is you're back.

44
00:05:50,759 --> 00:05:52,519
I've troubled you again.

45
00:05:52,759 --> 00:05:54,600
No need for such formalities with me.

46
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:57,600
If you ever find yourself in trouble again

47
00:05:58,079 --> 00:05:59,000
you can always come to me.

48
00:06:13,839 --> 00:06:14,439
Lord.

49
00:06:16,519 --> 00:06:17,120
My Lord.

50
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,480
Wake up, Ye Xian.

51
00:06:20,759 --> 00:06:21,319
Ye Xian.

52
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:25,439
Move away.

53
00:06:25,959 --> 00:06:27,360
Lord, please wake up.

54
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:30,920
Where am I?

55
00:06:31,879 --> 00:06:32,720
You drank too much last night

56
00:06:32,879 --> 00:06:34,160
and slept here at the tavern again.

57
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:35,680
Lord, you must get up.

58
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:36,920
We need to head back to the Marquis's at once.

59
00:06:38,399 --> 00:06:39,199
I'm not going back.
My Lord,

60
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,639
I understand

61
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,439
you're like this because of Miss Gu.

62
00:06:43,439 --> 00:06:44,759
How many times have I told you

63
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:47,040
don't mention her to me.

64
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:48,600
This is the last time, I swear.

65
00:06:49,199 --> 00:06:50,199
Mrs. Gu is gravely ill.

66
00:06:50,319 --> 00:06:51,000
They even posted notices yesterday

67
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,040
seeking renowned physicians.

68
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:54,040
Why are you telling me this?

69
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:55,920
It's not like I have a renowned physician.

70
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:59,319
Unless my master were here.

71
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,720
But he's far away in the southwest.

72
00:07:01,879 --> 00:07:03,319
That's exactly what I was about to say.

73
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:04,680
Mr. Xiao has returned.

74
00:07:04,959 --> 00:07:05,560
What?

75
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:07,720
When did he get back?
Just last night.

76
00:07:10,199 --> 00:07:10,759
Lord.

77
00:07:20,079 --> 00:07:20,839
Master.

78
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:33,279
Greetings, Young Lord.

79
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:36,360
Thank you, Young Lord

80
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,879
for being willing to lend a hand.

81
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:40,040
I am beyond grateful.

82
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,120
Of course—

83
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:44,399
My Grace always repays malice with kindness.

84
00:07:48,399 --> 00:07:48,959
This is

85
00:07:48,959 --> 00:07:50,279
the Divine Healer Xiao I told you about.

86
00:07:50,959 --> 00:07:51,800
He's also my master.

87
00:07:53,319 --> 00:07:54,399
It's an honor to meet you, Healer Xiao.

88
00:07:55,519 --> 00:07:56,319
Miss Gu.

89
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,040
Right this way, please.

90
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,279
This is the prescription

91
00:08:17,439 --> 00:08:18,480
from the previous physician.

92
00:08:21,319 --> 00:08:22,639
This prescription is fine.

93
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:24,399
How long has she been taking it?

94
00:08:26,079 --> 00:08:28,240
About a month or so.

95
00:08:29,319 --> 00:08:30,399
By all accounts

96
00:08:30,399 --> 00:08:31,959
there should have been some improvement.

97
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:34,399
Why hasn't she shown any sign of recovery?

98
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:36,639
May I see the medicinal herbs?

99
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:38,679
Of course.

100
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,120
Nanny Zhao.

101
00:08:49,399 --> 00:08:50,559
That explains it.

102
00:08:51,159 --> 00:08:51,960
Master.
This is...

103
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:54,320
Rhubarb.

104
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:55,879
Rhubarb.
Rhubarb.

105
00:08:59,519 --> 00:09:00,559
This prescription

106
00:09:00,799 --> 00:09:01,759
doesn't call for rhubarb.

107
00:09:02,759 --> 00:09:04,240
Here lies the source of the ailment.

108
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,080
Rhubarb is cold in nature.

109
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:08,279
It's used to purge fire and cool the blood

110
00:09:08,519 --> 00:09:09,759
expel toxins and clear stasis.

111
00:09:10,919 --> 00:09:13,120
However, rhubarb is fiercely potent.

112
00:09:13,919 --> 00:09:15,360
Mrs. Gu is already frail

113
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:16,840
with a weak and cold spleen and stomach.

114
00:09:17,279 --> 00:09:18,240
The medicine she needs

115
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,600
works in the opposite direction of rhubarb.

116
00:09:20,039 --> 00:09:21,639
If taken over a long period

117
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,679
I fear it could be fatal.

118
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,759
If the prescription is sound,

119
00:09:31,759 --> 00:09:32,919
the herbs must have been tampered with.

120
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,039
It seems

121
00:09:35,519 --> 00:09:37,120
someone has been adding rhubarb

122
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:37,960
to the prescription.

123
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:41,879
Mrs. Gu's medicine—

124
00:09:42,279 --> 00:09:43,240
who usually picks it up?

125
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,399
Miss Gu,

126
00:09:44,919 --> 00:09:46,559
we always send someone from the General Services

127
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:48,320
to take the prescription to the pharmacy.

128
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,039
When it comes back, they hand it to me
or Molan.

129
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:51,919
As for brewing it
Molan and I

130
00:09:52,879 --> 00:09:53,679
take turns watching over it.

131
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,360
About this matter—

132
00:09:59,519 --> 00:10:00,919
not a single word is to leave this room.

133
00:10:01,679 --> 00:10:02,639
Yes,  Miss Gu.

134
00:10:03,279 --> 00:10:04,120
If Lord Gu
or Rong should ask

135
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:06,879
just say we consulted a new physician

136
00:10:07,159 --> 00:10:08,279
and he found nothing unusual either.

137
00:10:08,759 --> 00:10:09,360
Understood?
Understood.

138
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:13,639
Divine Healer Xiao.

139
00:10:14,399 --> 00:10:15,399
Given how things stand

140
00:10:15,759 --> 00:10:17,519
please speak plainly with me.

141
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,240
My mother—

142
00:10:21,679 --> 00:10:23,480
can she still be cured?

143
00:10:24,159 --> 00:10:25,679
Recovery is not difficult.

144
00:10:26,399 --> 00:10:29,039
But the root lies in excessive worry and rumination

145
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:30,279
which have turned into an ailment.

146
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:33,279
If she cannot open up her heart

147
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:35,159
even a temporary recovery

148
00:10:35,559 --> 00:10:36,840
would be like water without a source

149
00:10:37,279 --> 00:10:38,759
a tree without roots.

150
00:10:50,679 --> 00:10:51,399
Gu Jinzhao.

151
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:53,879
What's on your mind?

152
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,039
Will you investigate?

153
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:56,600
Of course I will.

154
00:10:56,919 --> 00:10:58,440
And I'll get to the bottom of it.

155
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,080
I knew you'd say that.

156
00:11:01,679 --> 00:11:02,320
So—
do you have the people for it?

157
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,440
If not

158
00:11:04,639 --> 00:11:05,879
I can lend you Li Xianhuai.

159
00:11:06,679 --> 00:11:07,519
Not just yet.

160
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,879
This time I definitely won't do anything rash.

161
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,519
So don't overthink it.

162
00:11:13,759 --> 00:11:15,039
I have to find the culprit first

163
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,519
and then I'll trouble you for help.

164
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,399
You've got it all figured out.

165
00:11:19,919 --> 00:11:20,519
Fine then.
I'm off.

166
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:24,799
Ye Xian.

167
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,080
Thank you.

168
00:11:56,519 --> 00:11:57,480
Miss Gu, honestly—

169
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,080
Since you've run into him anyway

170
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:00,879
why are you hiding over here?

171
00:12:01,279 --> 00:12:02,519
Even just greeting Young Lord

172
00:12:02,519 --> 00:12:03,720
would have been the proper thing to do.

173
00:12:15,399 --> 00:12:16,480
What's there to see?

174
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:18,679
Young Lord has eyes only for Jinzhao.

175
00:12:18,879 --> 00:12:20,080
He doesn't even notice anyone else.

176
00:12:20,919 --> 00:12:22,519
I've no desire to make a fool of myself again.

177
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:35,399
Luo Liu, go.

178
00:12:35,759 --> 00:12:36,600
Quickly, take this prescription
and get the herbs.

179
00:12:37,159 --> 00:12:37,559
Yes.

180
00:12:39,679 --> 00:12:40,840
Hurry, hurry up.

181
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:43,000
Sir, your medicine is ready.

182
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:44,960
Take care now.

183
00:12:49,879 --> 00:12:51,000
What took you so long?

184
00:12:51,759 --> 00:12:52,960
Are you trying to get yourself killed?

185
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:53,960
Where is it?

186
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:11,679
Look.

187
00:13:12,039 --> 00:13:13,559
Just as I thought—rhubarb in every packet.

188
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:14,679
That concubine Song

189
00:13:14,679 --> 00:13:15,840
truly has a vicious heart.

190
00:13:18,159 --> 00:13:19,159
You saw it all clearly?

191
00:13:20,159 --> 00:13:21,120
Crystal clear.

192
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:22,799
It was from Concubine Song's quarters—

193
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:23,799
Liuxiang and Luo Liu.

194
00:13:27,919 --> 00:13:29,440
Ah, this wine...

195
00:13:42,759 --> 00:13:44,399
This girl's quite something.

196
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:11,519
Thank you for your help, Guard Li.

197
00:14:11,919 --> 00:14:13,720
Please, on behalf of my lady

198
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:15,039
convey a message to Young Lord.

199
00:14:16,519 --> 00:14:17,600
Just frighten them a bit

200
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:18,919
no need for actual punishment.

201
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:20,360
I understand, sir.

202
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:26,320
Before the midday meal

203
00:14:26,759 --> 00:14:29,000
Mrs. Mu paid a sudden visit.

204
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:32,440
She came about her eldest son's marriage.

205
00:14:32,679 --> 00:14:33,480
Mu Zhidi.

206
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:34,080
Yes.

207
00:14:34,679 --> 00:14:37,240
That tall, dull-witted one.

208
00:14:37,480 --> 00:14:38,759
Xuanqing's classmate.

209
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:43,600
This rose dew is so fresh and sweet.

210
00:14:43,759 --> 00:14:44,519
Have a taste.
Alright.

211
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:49,159
So this Mu Zhidi and the marriage proposal—

212
00:14:49,399 --> 00:14:50,519
what did she say to you?

213
00:14:51,919 --> 00:14:52,720
Could it be

214
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:54,399
she's taken a liking to our Yanying?

215
00:14:54,639 --> 00:14:55,799
Not Yanying.

216
00:14:55,799 --> 00:14:56,960
It's Miss Gu.

217
00:14:58,240 --> 00:15:00,600
It was last year, during the chrysanthemum viewing.

218
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:02,720
He seemed perfectly quiet at the time

219
00:15:03,279 --> 00:15:04,799
but apparently he'd already fallen for her.

220
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:07,840
They say from that very day

221
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:09,559
he couldn't get her out of his mind.

222
00:15:10,440 --> 00:15:11,720
Then a few days ago

223
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:14,879
when the family brought up arranging his marriage

224
00:15:16,240 --> 00:15:18,440
he could no longer hold it in and confessed.

225
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:21,279
When the Mus heard she's a daughter of a concubine

226
00:15:22,039 --> 00:15:23,559
they said absolutely not.

227
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:25,039
What do you mean?
A concubine's daughter?

228
00:15:26,159 --> 00:15:27,960
The second daughter of the Gu family.

229
00:15:28,279 --> 00:15:29,320
The one they call Lan.

230
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:32,200
Born of a concubine, indeed.

231
00:15:33,879 --> 00:15:35,919
But that Mu Zhidi, of all people

232
00:15:35,919 --> 00:15:37,240
is a stubborn romantic.

233
00:15:38,240 --> 00:15:39,440
He actually put on

234
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:42,000
a "I'll marry no one but the Lan" act.

235
00:15:42,879 --> 00:15:44,759
Mrs. Mu was at her wits' end

236
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:47,240
so she came around asking questions

237
00:15:47,759 --> 00:15:48,960
wanting to find out

238
00:15:49,360 --> 00:15:50,960
what sort of person

239
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:53,320
this Lan really is.

240
00:15:54,159 --> 00:15:55,559
Honestly, that Mrs. Mu

241
00:15:55,559 --> 00:15:56,840
has no sense of direction at all.

242
00:15:57,720 --> 00:16:00,120
She went on and on about the Lan

243
00:16:01,320 --> 00:16:04,080
then suddenly started asking about Jinzhao as well.

244
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:06,960
Go on, eat.

245
00:16:09,879 --> 00:16:10,720
I've had enough.

246
00:16:12,039 --> 00:16:13,759
Why is she asking around about Jinzhao?

247
00:16:14,159 --> 00:16:15,080
She says

248
00:16:15,559 --> 00:16:18,159
she's heard Jinzhao is a great beauty

249
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:20,480
with a generous dowry

250
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:22,000
and the firstborn of the lawful wife.

251
00:16:23,360 --> 00:16:25,799
A perfect match for their Mu Zhidi.

252
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:27,679
And since

253
00:16:27,679 --> 00:16:29,879
I have a connection with Old Mrs. Ji

254
00:16:30,559 --> 00:16:32,799
she wanted to ask me to play matchmaker.

255
00:16:34,559 --> 00:16:35,519
Tell me—

256
00:16:36,039 --> 00:16:38,240
is this match suitable or not?

257
00:16:38,440 --> 00:16:39,440
It's not.

258
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:41,679
The Mu Zhidi clearly has his eye on

259
00:16:41,679 --> 00:16:42,559
the Lan.

260
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:44,000
But Mrs. Mu is trying to twist it

261
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:44,879
into the eldest Miss Gu.

262
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:46,759
What status does she think her family holds?

263
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:48,159
And what does she take the Gu family for?

264
00:16:48,600 --> 00:16:49,720
It's utterly absurd.

265
00:16:51,919 --> 00:16:52,679
This matter—

266
00:16:53,039 --> 00:16:53,639
you needn't

267
00:16:53,639 --> 00:16:54,720
bring it up with Mrs. Ji.

268
00:16:55,240 --> 00:16:55,840
It would only

269
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:57,399
upset people for no good reason.

270
00:16:57,639 --> 00:17:00,279
I'm consulting you first, aren't I?

271
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:03,600
And I wasn't really going to do it.

272
00:17:04,119 --> 00:17:04,920
That's fine then.

273
00:17:06,200 --> 00:17:07,440
I have other matters to attend to.

274
00:17:07,839 --> 00:17:08,839
I'll take my leave now.

275
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:12,279
Please enjoy your meal, Mother.

276
00:17:17,079 --> 00:17:18,559
What's gotten into him?

277
00:17:18,880 --> 00:17:19,880
From what I can tell

278
00:17:20,039 --> 00:17:21,599
He seems angered.

279
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:24,200
That much I've noticed myself.

280
00:17:24,960 --> 00:17:26,400
But what is he angry about?

281
00:17:31,359 --> 00:17:31,960
Lord.

282
00:17:34,119 --> 00:17:35,519
Go and discreetly find out

283
00:17:35,960 --> 00:17:37,799
what's really going on with the Mu family

284
00:17:37,799 --> 00:17:38,880
proposing to the Gu household.

285
00:17:40,599 --> 00:17:41,039
Yes.

286
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:55,079
Help!

287
00:17:55,559 --> 00:17:56,960
Help!

288
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:08,599
Speak.

289
00:18:09,640 --> 00:18:11,039
How did you slip the drug

290
00:18:11,039 --> 00:18:12,119
to poison your mistress?

291
00:18:12,799 --> 00:18:14,160
Confess truthfully.

292
00:18:17,599 --> 00:18:19,000
I did no such thing!

293
00:18:21,880 --> 00:18:23,119
Still trying to deny it?

294
00:18:24,920 --> 00:18:26,559
Luo Liu has already confessed everything.

295
00:18:27,720 --> 00:18:30,240
He said you told him to add rhubarb to the medicine.

296
00:18:30,240 --> 00:18:31,240
I didn't!
Then who?

297
00:18:39,319 --> 00:18:40,640
It was Nanny Zhou.

298
00:18:41,680 --> 00:18:43,200
Nanny Zhou told me

299
00:18:43,440 --> 00:18:45,119
to give the herbs to Luo Liu.

300
00:18:54,319 --> 00:18:54,960
Lord.

301
00:18:55,880 --> 00:18:56,359
They confessed.

302
00:18:56,559 --> 00:18:57,440
Both of them confessed fully.

303
00:18:57,640 --> 00:18:58,559
We didn't even have time to frighten them.

304
00:18:58,680 --> 00:18:59,440
They just spilled everything.

305
00:19:09,319 --> 00:19:09,839
Let's go.
To find Gu Jinzhao.

306
00:19:10,839 --> 00:19:11,200
Yes.
The Marquis arrives!

307
00:19:45,799 --> 00:19:46,759
Greetings, Your Lordship.

308
00:19:52,400 --> 00:19:53,880
I heard you've seized two people

309
00:19:54,240 --> 00:19:56,000
and set up your own private court here.

310
00:19:57,960 --> 00:19:58,519
Helping a friend

311
00:19:58,519 --> 00:19:59,559
interrogate a couple of household servants, that's all.

312
00:20:00,440 --> 00:20:01,279
No torture was used.

313
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:27,000
What utter nonsense.

314
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:29,359
Which one of your lowlife friends is it this time?

315
00:20:30,880 --> 00:20:32,720
Even if I told you, you wouldn't know them.

316
00:20:33,240 --> 00:20:34,279
And if I pointed them out

317
00:20:34,839 --> 00:20:35,920
your arm wouldn't reach that far.

318
00:20:36,559 --> 00:20:37,200
Insolence!

319
00:20:38,759 --> 00:20:40,000
Just looking at this confession

320
00:20:40,279 --> 00:20:42,079
it's clearly one of those degenerate households

321
00:20:42,079 --> 00:20:43,720
with corrupt morals and low breeding.

322
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:46,240
You spend your days carousing with them

323
00:20:46,240 --> 00:20:47,079
stirring up trouble.

324
00:20:47,519 --> 00:20:48,519
Do you not care about your future at all?

325
00:20:50,400 --> 00:20:52,319
You make it sound as if I'd have a future

326
00:20:52,680 --> 00:20:53,440
if I stopped carousing
and stirring up trouble.

327
00:20:55,839 --> 00:20:56,359
Lord.

328
00:20:56,960 --> 00:20:57,480
My Lord.
Sir, please calm yourself down.

329
00:20:58,519 --> 00:20:59,960
Young master spoke in a moment of anger.

330
00:21:01,480 --> 00:21:02,839
He doesn't need you to plead his case.

331
00:21:03,960 --> 00:21:05,000
I know exactly what he is

332
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:06,119
better than anyone.

333
00:21:06,839 --> 00:21:07,440
Guards.

334
00:21:08,359 --> 00:21:09,319
Keep an eye on this brat.

335
00:21:09,599 --> 00:21:10,720
Without my express order

336
00:21:11,240 --> 00:21:13,079
he is not to take a single step beyond the Marquis's gates.

337
00:21:13,279 --> 00:21:13,920
As you command.

338
00:21:17,240 --> 00:21:17,960
Master Xiao.
Come with me.

339
00:21:19,720 --> 00:21:20,599
I have something to ask you.

340
00:21:21,079 --> 00:21:21,680
Yes.

341
00:21:32,839 --> 00:21:34,400
What you said just now is true?

342
00:21:35,559 --> 00:21:37,079
I practiced medicine in the southwest for many years.

343
00:21:37,519 --> 00:21:38,839
I saved the lives of several bandits.

344
00:21:39,559 --> 00:21:40,839
They would not keep the truth from me.

345
00:21:41,759 --> 00:21:43,640
Their leader told me himself

346
00:21:44,559 --> 00:21:46,039
that their entire families

347
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:47,440
are held hostage by Prince Glorian.

348
00:21:47,880 --> 00:21:49,359
He forced them to assassinate the Crown Prince.

349
00:21:53,400 --> 00:21:55,279
Without Prince Glorian working from the inside

350
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:56,799
those bandits could never

351
00:21:56,799 --> 00:21:59,119
have concealed themselves in the capital for so long—

352
00:21:59,680 --> 00:22:01,680
let alone learn the Crown Prince's movements.

353
00:22:02,160 --> 00:22:03,039
Years ago,

354
00:22:03,559 --> 00:22:05,279
I believed that eliminating Prince Chengqing

355
00:22:05,359 --> 00:22:06,440
would mean Prince Glorian—

356
00:22:06,440 --> 00:22:08,079
his brother from the same mother—

357
00:22:09,119 --> 00:22:10,880
would surely not remain either.

358
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:13,759
But His Majesty, in his mercy, spared him.

359
00:22:20,759 --> 00:22:21,599
From this day forward

360
00:22:21,799 --> 00:22:22,839
set aside all other tasks.

361
00:22:22,960 --> 00:22:25,160
Focus solely on surveilling Prince Glorian's residence in secret.

362
00:22:25,400 --> 00:22:26,519
At the first sign of trouble

363
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:28,079
report it to me immediately.

364
00:22:28,960 --> 00:22:30,640
What is it that worries You?

365
00:22:36,200 --> 00:22:37,279
His Majesty is gravely ill.

366
00:22:37,839 --> 00:22:39,119
I fear that rogue

367
00:22:39,400 --> 00:22:40,400
will try something.

368
00:22:41,759 --> 00:22:43,079
Xiaoyou understands.

369
00:23:05,400 --> 00:23:06,599
You've worked hard.

370
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:09,359
Lan, you too.

371
00:23:09,519 --> 00:23:10,519
I didn't do much, Mother.

372
00:23:10,799 --> 00:23:12,119
Jinzhao did all the real work.

373
00:23:12,519 --> 00:23:13,599
The Divine Healer Xiao this time—

374
00:23:13,599 --> 00:23:14,440
she's the one who brought him here.

375
00:23:15,160 --> 00:23:16,799
Those days you were unconscious

376
00:23:16,960 --> 00:23:18,920
Jinzhao watched over you day and night.

377
00:23:19,240 --> 00:23:20,680
She's only just gone to rest a little.

378
00:23:22,720 --> 00:23:24,000
You are both good children.

379
00:23:25,119 --> 00:23:26,240
All of this for me.

380
00:23:27,400 --> 00:23:28,559
I am fine now.

381
00:23:28,960 --> 00:23:30,119
Go and get some rest yourselves.

382
00:23:30,680 --> 00:23:31,519
Off you go now.

383
00:23:44,319 --> 00:23:45,880
What's written here—

384
00:23:46,559 --> 00:23:47,680
is it all true?

385
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:49,359
Signed, sealed, everything in order.

386
00:23:49,759 --> 00:23:50,799
If you don't believe it,

387
00:23:51,160 --> 00:23:52,000
the culprits are tied up right here.

388
00:23:52,240 --> 00:23:53,519
You can question them again yourself.

389
00:23:54,200 --> 00:23:55,079
Guards.

390
00:23:56,799 --> 00:23:57,920
Bring Concubine Song

391
00:23:57,920 --> 00:23:59,720
and Nanny Zhou here.

392
00:24:00,119 --> 00:24:00,720
Yes.

393
00:24:06,400 --> 00:24:07,279
This here—

394
00:24:08,279 --> 00:24:09,839
your favorite pigeon soup.

395
00:24:10,039 --> 00:24:11,400
I simmered it a full four hours.

396
00:24:11,920 --> 00:24:12,799
Have at least a little.

397
00:24:16,680 --> 00:24:17,319
Here.

398
00:24:17,559 --> 00:24:18,400
My Lady.
Concubine Song.

399
00:24:20,920 --> 00:24:22,279
Nanny Zhou was taken to the front courtyard

400
00:24:22,279 --> 00:24:23,599
by the Master's men.

401
00:24:24,240 --> 00:24:25,839
Why would the Master take Nanny Zhou?

402
00:24:25,960 --> 00:24:27,000
I don't know.

403
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:28,400
I only saw a few old serving women

404
00:24:28,400 --> 00:24:29,480
dragging Nanny Zhou away

405
00:24:29,480 --> 00:24:30,720
fierce as demons.

406
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:31,839
It didn't look good at all.

407
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:36,359
What has Nanny Zhou done this time?

408
00:24:38,680 --> 00:24:39,279
Mother.

409
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:40,519
Mother.

410
00:24:41,440 --> 00:24:42,759
You know something, don't you?

411
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:45,640
No, I don't.

412
00:24:46,759 --> 00:24:48,240
Is Concubine Song here?

413
00:24:49,440 --> 00:24:50,039
Lan.
Lan.

414
00:24:52,839 --> 00:24:54,359
Ziling, go and stop them.

415
00:24:54,480 --> 00:24:55,240
Don't let them in.
Yes, My Lady.

416
00:25:02,200 --> 00:25:03,279
What's really going on?

417
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:06,079
Say something.

418
00:25:06,640 --> 00:25:07,359
Lan, I...

419
00:25:14,160 --> 00:25:14,519
Move aside.

420
00:25:24,960 --> 00:25:26,279
You can read.

421
00:25:26,880 --> 00:25:28,720
Luo Liu and Liuxiang have both confessed.

422
00:25:29,799 --> 00:25:31,160
They say you put them up to it.

423
00:25:32,359 --> 00:25:33,799
Do you admit it or not?

424
00:25:37,799 --> 00:25:38,680
I admit it.

425
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:40,160
Everything

426
00:25:40,839 --> 00:25:42,200
was all done at my bidding.

427
00:25:43,119 --> 00:25:44,920
How utterly vicious.

428
00:25:45,920 --> 00:25:47,279
What did the Mistress ever do to you

429
00:25:47,640 --> 00:25:48,519
that you could commit

430
00:25:48,519 --> 00:25:50,960
such a heinous, unhinged act?

431
00:25:51,240 --> 00:25:52,400
Lord Gu,

432
00:25:53,359 --> 00:25:53,799
Nanny Zhou

433
00:25:53,799 --> 00:25:54,960
is nothing but a lowly servant.

434
00:25:55,599 --> 00:25:57,119
What grudge could she possibly hold against the Mistress?

435
00:25:57,359 --> 00:25:58,680
She had to be acting on someone's orders.

436
00:25:58,799 --> 00:25:59,960
Ms. Jinzhao, don't make reckless accusations.

437
00:26:00,599 --> 00:26:01,440
No one put me up to it.

438
00:26:01,759 --> 00:26:02,559
It was all

439
00:26:02,559 --> 00:26:03,640
my decision alone.

440
00:26:04,480 --> 00:26:05,160
Lord Gu.

441
00:26:05,359 --> 00:26:07,079
Concubine Song is just outside.

442
00:26:07,079 --> 00:26:07,960
Bring her in.

443
00:26:08,200 --> 00:26:08,799
Qingpu.

444
00:26:09,240 --> 00:26:09,960
Gag her.
Yes.

445
00:26:31,279 --> 00:26:31,920
Lord Gu.

446
00:26:32,240 --> 00:26:33,000
What is all this?
Such a grand commotion.

447
00:26:33,720 --> 00:26:35,440
You know perfectly well what this is about, don't you?

448
00:26:35,960 --> 00:26:36,440
I—

449
00:26:37,960 --> 00:26:39,039
I don't understand.

450
00:26:39,839 --> 00:26:40,720
Then let me ask you.

451
00:26:41,960 --> 00:26:44,200
Nanny Zhou instructed Liuxiang

452
00:26:44,480 --> 00:26:47,200
to pass the rhubarb to Luo Liu

453
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:49,000
to mix into the Madam's medicine.

454
00:26:49,759 --> 00:26:52,400
Were you the one behind it?

455
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,039
Listen to me.

456
00:26:57,519 --> 00:26:59,319
From beginning to end—

457
00:26:59,319 --> 00:27:00,240
you knew nothing about this.

458
00:27:00,640 --> 00:27:01,359
What medicine?

459
00:27:01,480 --> 00:27:03,200
What… what Luo Liu?

460
00:27:03,559 --> 00:27:04,279
It was all Nanny Zhou
and the people she hired.

461
00:27:05,599 --> 00:27:06,279
No matter where you are—

462
00:27:06,519 --> 00:27:07,920
even if you end up before the Shuntian Prefecture—

463
00:27:08,240 --> 00:27:10,119
you must say, that from start to finish

464
00:27:10,119 --> 00:27:11,119
you knew absolutely nothing.

465
00:27:13,000 --> 00:27:13,880
Lan, but I—
No "buts."

466
00:27:15,200 --> 00:27:16,559
We are at a critical juncture now.

467
00:27:17,599 --> 00:27:18,720
Do you want to die?

468
00:27:20,599 --> 00:27:21,720
Think of me!

469
00:27:22,319 --> 00:27:23,920
If you die, what will become of me?

470
00:27:24,240 --> 00:27:24,880
Mother.

471
00:27:25,640 --> 00:27:27,319
Think of me—please, think of me.

472
00:27:29,839 --> 00:27:31,240
I wasn't the one behind it, Lord Gu.

473
00:27:31,559 --> 00:27:32,359
I know nothing about it.
Is that so?

474
00:27:35,039 --> 00:27:36,799
But Nanny Zhou just confessed.

475
00:27:37,200 --> 00:27:38,720
She said it was you who gave the order.

476
00:27:42,920 --> 00:27:43,799
She's lying!
Lying?

477
00:27:46,039 --> 00:27:47,200
Why would she lie?

478
00:27:47,960 --> 00:27:48,880
She plotted against the Madam

479
00:27:49,039 --> 00:27:50,119
and it was all because of you, wasn't it?

480
00:27:50,759 --> 00:27:51,680
Liuxiang—
Nanny Zhou—

481
00:27:52,759 --> 00:27:54,119
both of them are from your own quarters.

482
00:27:54,759 --> 00:27:56,359
And you dare claim you knew nothing

483
00:27:56,480 --> 00:27:57,480
about any of this?

484
00:27:57,839 --> 00:27:58,799
Ms. Jinzhao.

485
00:27:59,079 --> 00:28:00,519
I truly knew nothing.

486
00:28:00,640 --> 00:28:01,680
Still clinging to your story?

487
00:28:03,440 --> 00:28:05,039
Then we'll have to take this to the Shuntian Prefecture.

488
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:19,599
Nanny Zhou was your wet nurse.

489
00:28:20,079 --> 00:28:22,079
Liuxiang was your personal maid.

490
00:28:22,440 --> 00:28:23,519
They committed such

491
00:28:23,519 --> 00:28:24,640
utterly villainous acts

492
00:28:24,640 --> 00:28:25,920
and yet you claim to know nothing?

493
00:28:26,039 --> 00:28:27,880
How utterly foolish can you be?

494
00:28:28,720 --> 00:28:29,920
From now on, you are not to leave your quarters.

495
00:28:30,119 --> 00:28:32,279
Confine yourself and reflect upon your misdeeds.

496
00:28:32,279 --> 00:28:32,799
Lord Gu

497
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:34,000
As for the rest of you—
Liuxiang.

498
00:28:35,240 --> 00:28:35,920
Luo Liu.

499
00:28:36,880 --> 00:28:38,599
Forty strokes each.

500
00:28:38,720 --> 00:28:39,400
When that's done

501
00:28:40,039 --> 00:28:41,640
throw them onto the estate for hard labor.

502
00:28:41,920 --> 00:28:42,599
Nanny Zhou.

503
00:28:43,279 --> 00:28:44,559
Sixty strokes.

504
00:28:44,559 --> 00:28:45,880
Make every stroke count.

505
00:28:45,880 --> 00:28:46,279
Lord Gu.

506
00:28:46,440 --> 00:28:48,279
Send her to the estate as well when it's over.

507
00:28:48,279 --> 00:28:49,000
A moment, Lord Gu.

508
00:28:50,160 --> 00:28:51,720
She nearly drove the Madam to her death.

509
00:28:51,720 --> 00:28:53,319
And her punishment is merely confinement?

510
00:28:53,480 --> 00:28:54,920
Did Nanny Zhou not just say

511
00:28:55,680 --> 00:28:57,440
that she alone was behind it all?

512
00:28:57,440 --> 00:28:59,960
Concubine Song knew nothing of it.

513
00:28:59,960 --> 00:29:01,119
Those words you just spoke—

514
00:29:01,279 --> 00:29:02,319
do you even believe them yourself?

515
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:03,519
Nanny Zhou

516
00:29:03,519 --> 00:29:04,920
slipped rhubarb into the Madam's medicine

517
00:29:05,559 --> 00:29:06,839
all because of Concubine Song, did she not?

518
00:29:07,359 --> 00:29:08,640
Liuxiang already confessed

519
00:29:09,119 --> 00:29:10,519
that since the tenth month of last year

520
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:12,799
they have been tampering with the Madam's medicine.

521
00:29:13,279 --> 00:29:14,480
All this time

522
00:29:14,720 --> 00:29:15,359
Concubine Song—

523
00:29:15,359 --> 00:29:16,720
how could she possibly know nothing?

524
00:29:16,799 --> 00:29:18,039
And what of it?

525
00:29:18,799 --> 00:29:19,759
In judgment and in household governance

526
00:29:19,920 --> 00:29:21,240
one cannot rely on mere supposition.

527
00:29:21,799 --> 00:29:23,359
You go on about the Shuntian Prefecture—

528
00:29:24,519 --> 00:29:25,640
but in Liuxiang's deposition

529
00:29:25,640 --> 00:29:26,559
there is no mention of Concubine Song.

530
00:29:26,720 --> 00:29:27,759
Nanny Zhou, too, says

531
00:29:27,759 --> 00:29:29,240
Concubine Song knew nothing.

532
00:29:29,519 --> 00:29:30,559
Since there is no proof

533
00:29:31,319 --> 00:29:32,880
even the Shuntian Prefecture

534
00:29:32,880 --> 00:29:34,559
could only rule the same way.

535
00:29:35,400 --> 00:29:36,680
Since you say there is no proof

536
00:29:37,519 --> 00:29:38,279
then I will go now
and search Concubine Song's quarters.

537
00:29:39,640 --> 00:29:40,680
I refuse to believe I won't find something.

538
00:29:40,920 --> 00:29:41,640
Qingpu—and Nanny Zhou—
we're leaving.

539
00:29:42,720 --> 00:29:43,440
Yes, My Lady.
You—

540
00:29:50,200 --> 00:29:51,240
What are you standing there for?

541
00:29:51,640 --> 00:29:52,519
Drag them away, quickly.

542
00:29:52,920 --> 00:29:54,240
Lord Gu, Lord Gu.

543
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:55,480
Lord Gu, you mustn't!
Sixty strokes

544
00:29:56,039 --> 00:29:57,240
will be the death of Nanny Zhou!

545
00:29:57,240 --> 00:29:57,920
Lord Gu

546
00:29:57,920 --> 00:29:59,119
I beg you, Lord Gu!

547
00:29:59,119 --> 00:30:00,400
Can't bear to part with Nanny Zhou?

548
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:02,000
Perhaps you'd like to join her?

549
00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:03,720
Think of your daughter Lan.

550
00:30:03,839 --> 00:30:04,519
For goodness' sake.

551
00:30:05,319 --> 00:30:06,079
Take them away now.

552
00:30:13,119 --> 00:30:14,519
What are we going to do?

553
00:30:20,599 --> 00:30:21,559
Concubine Song's quarters—

554
00:30:21,680 --> 00:30:22,640
there's probably nothing there.

555
00:30:24,160 --> 00:30:25,200
Should we still go, then?

556
00:30:26,519 --> 00:30:27,319
You go ahead.

557
00:30:27,599 --> 00:30:29,000
I'll make one more attempt to probe Concubine Song.

558
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:51,160
What do you want now?

559
00:30:51,279 --> 00:30:51,880
Nanny Zhou

560
00:30:51,880 --> 00:30:53,440
slipped rhubarb into the Madam's medicine.

561
00:30:54,279 --> 00:30:55,359
You knew all along—

562
00:30:55,839 --> 00:30:57,000
you were the one who ordered it.

563
00:30:57,839 --> 00:30:58,519
Weren't you?
No.

564
00:31:01,039 --> 00:31:02,000
I don't know anything.

565
00:31:03,599 --> 00:31:04,519
Nanny Zhou

566
00:31:05,160 --> 00:31:06,240
has been sentenced to sixty strokes.

567
00:31:07,359 --> 00:31:08,799
On the estate, there is little medicine and no proper care—

568
00:31:09,480 --> 00:31:10,359
it is very likely

569
00:31:10,720 --> 00:31:12,119
she may never come back from this.

570
00:31:14,279 --> 00:31:16,079
If you are willing to tell the truth

571
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:18,759
I can guarantee she will survive.

572
00:31:20,519 --> 00:31:22,279
You and Nanny Zhou are as close as mother and daughter.

573
00:31:23,279 --> 00:31:24,440
Everything she did

574
00:31:25,119 --> 00:31:26,079
was for your sake.

575
00:31:27,039 --> 00:31:28,079
Can you truly bear

576
00:31:28,680 --> 00:31:30,440
to watch her go to her death?

577
00:31:33,960 --> 00:31:34,759
Gu Jinzhao.

578
00:31:37,039 --> 00:31:37,680
Lan.

579
00:31:38,279 --> 00:31:39,599
My mother knows nothing.

580
00:31:39,839 --> 00:31:40,680
She did nothing.
Nothing at all.

581
00:31:41,640 --> 00:31:42,359
Then why so defensive?

582
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:43,960
I am not defensive.

583
00:31:44,480 --> 00:31:45,680
It's you who won't stop hounding us.

584
00:31:45,920 --> 00:31:46,759
You know full well
that Nanny Zhou will never

585
00:31:47,759 --> 00:31:48,640
come back in this lifetime.

586
00:31:49,119 --> 00:31:50,319
Why are you still not satisfied?

587
00:31:51,039 --> 00:31:52,480
What exactly do you want?

588
00:31:53,039 --> 00:31:54,559
My mother is Father's concubine.

589
00:31:54,839 --> 00:31:55,799
How she is to be dealt with

590
00:31:55,920 --> 00:31:57,160
is for Father alone to decide.

591
00:31:57,599 --> 00:31:58,920
There's no need for you to usurp that authority.

592
00:31:59,279 --> 00:32:00,079
Lan.

593
00:32:03,319 --> 00:32:04,039
Ms. Jinzhao.

594
00:32:04,359 --> 00:32:05,799
I truly know nothing.

595
00:32:06,119 --> 00:32:07,119
You are overthinking this.

596
00:32:07,400 --> 00:32:08,079
Mother.

597
00:32:08,799 --> 00:32:09,680
No need to explain to her.

598
00:32:10,119 --> 00:32:11,039
This household—

599
00:32:11,319 --> 00:32:13,000
she is not yet the one in charge.

600
00:32:19,519 --> 00:32:20,160
Ms. Jinzhao

601
00:32:22,000 --> 00:32:23,440
We found nothing at all.

602
00:32:26,880 --> 00:32:27,720
Are you alright?

603
00:32:29,599 --> 00:32:30,160
I'm fine.

604
00:32:32,759 --> 00:32:33,759
I was just thinking

605
00:32:34,680 --> 00:32:35,960
about what Gu Lan said.

606
00:32:37,440 --> 00:32:38,359
She was right.

607
00:32:39,200 --> 00:32:40,039
This household

608
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:42,359
Is indeed not mine to rule.

609
00:32:44,720 --> 00:32:45,880
But so what?

610
00:32:47,839 --> 00:32:49,519
Regardless of who holds sway over this house

611
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:52,960
the truth between right and wrong can never be overturned.

612
00:32:56,559 --> 00:32:57,559
Lord Gu is inside.

613
00:32:58,519 --> 00:33:00,519
Nanny Zhou received sixty strokes

614
00:33:01,119 --> 00:33:02,440
and has been banished to the estate.

615
00:33:03,240 --> 00:33:05,200
She likely won't last much longer.

616
00:33:05,960 --> 00:33:06,880
That counts as

617
00:33:07,279 --> 00:33:08,519
avenging you, in a way.

618
00:33:10,359 --> 00:33:11,519
And what of Song Miaohua?

619
00:33:12,440 --> 00:33:15,240
Concubine Song genuinely knew nothing.

620
00:33:15,599 --> 00:33:17,279
It was all at Nanny Zhou's instigation.

621
00:33:20,839 --> 00:33:22,880
I'd like to ask you for a favor.

622
00:33:24,720 --> 00:33:26,079
Concubine Song is, after all

623
00:33:26,079 --> 00:33:27,559
Lan's mother.

624
00:33:28,400 --> 00:33:29,680
Even setting her aside

625
00:33:30,160 --> 00:33:31,039
we must at least

626
00:33:31,400 --> 00:33:33,240
consider Lan's standing, mustn't we?

627
00:33:36,519 --> 00:33:38,319
In the end, Lord Gu still cannot bear to part with her.

628
00:33:40,240 --> 00:33:41,640
It's no wonder Song Miaohua

629
00:33:41,640 --> 00:33:43,119
gave up even her own parents back then

630
00:33:43,960 --> 00:33:45,400
just to be with His Lordship.

631
00:33:45,960 --> 00:33:46,519
Oh, you.

632
00:33:47,240 --> 00:33:49,160
I'm speaking with you calmly, aren't I?

633
00:33:56,319 --> 00:33:57,240
It's getting late.

634
00:33:57,400 --> 00:33:58,160
You should rest now.

635
00:34:16,480 --> 00:34:17,239
Madam.

636
00:34:18,840 --> 00:34:20,079
I owe you everything this time.

637
00:34:22,880 --> 00:34:24,239
They told me what happened.

638
00:34:24,840 --> 00:34:25,840
If not for you

639
00:34:26,679 --> 00:34:28,039
I might have truly

640
00:34:28,719 --> 00:34:29,519
this time

641
00:34:29,519 --> 00:34:31,039
been killed by Song Miaohua.

642
00:34:31,679 --> 00:34:32,519
Don't dwell on any of that.
Put those matters aside.

643
00:34:34,119 --> 00:34:35,199
What matters most right now

644
00:34:35,679 --> 00:34:36,880
is that you focus on recovering in peace.

645
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:39,119
I'll take care of everything else.

646
00:34:49,239 --> 00:34:50,199
You may all leave us.

647
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:51,840
I have something to say to Nanny Zhou.

648
00:34:58,960 --> 00:34:59,960
Lan.

649
00:35:02,639 --> 00:35:03,440
Nanny Zhou.

650
00:35:04,599 --> 00:35:06,039
My mother has been confined.

651
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:07,239
She can't come out.

652
00:35:08,280 --> 00:35:09,519
I came on her behalf to see you.

653
00:35:11,360 --> 00:35:12,400
It's better this way.

654
00:35:14,639 --> 00:35:16,039
That you've come to send me off—

655
00:35:17,599 --> 00:35:19,119
it makes me glad, too.

656
00:35:20,039 --> 00:35:21,800
But now that I'm leaving

657
00:35:22,199 --> 00:35:24,280
you must take good care of your mother.

658
00:35:26,039 --> 00:35:29,599
I truly fear she'll suffer without me.

659
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:34,719
I'll take good care of her.

660
00:35:35,719 --> 00:35:36,840
Don't worry.

661
00:35:38,440 --> 00:35:39,400
Little Blackbird.

662
00:35:39,400 --> 00:35:40,679
Quick, say something nice.

663
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:42,280
Good fortune and blessings.

664
00:35:42,400 --> 00:35:43,840
Good fortune and blessings.

665
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:49,039
Madam.

666
00:35:49,880 --> 00:35:51,159
Have you ever considered

667
00:35:51,400 --> 00:35:52,679
parting ways with the Lord Gu?

668
00:35:53,559 --> 00:35:54,320
What?

669
00:35:55,320 --> 00:35:56,639
This whole business—

670
00:35:56,880 --> 00:35:58,119
I've thought it through carefully.

671
00:35:58,960 --> 00:35:59,760
On the surface

672
00:35:59,760 --> 00:36:01,159
it looks like Concubine Song and Nanny Zhou

673
00:36:01,400 --> 00:36:02,519
out of jealousy and spite

674
00:36:02,840 --> 00:36:04,400
slipped rhubarb into your medicine.

675
00:36:04,840 --> 00:36:06,360
But the reason they dared do such a thing

676
00:36:06,920 --> 00:36:08,320
is because they could clearly see

677
00:36:10,119 --> 00:36:11,519
that between you and the Lord Gu

678
00:36:12,079 --> 00:36:13,079
there is a rift.

679
00:36:15,760 --> 00:36:16,719
The Lord Gu knew full well

680
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:18,719
that Concubine Song must have known

681
00:36:18,719 --> 00:36:19,920
what Nanny Zhou was doing.

682
00:36:20,400 --> 00:36:21,880
Yet she received no punishment whatsoever—

683
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:24,039
merely a cursory brush-off.

684
00:36:25,679 --> 00:36:26,519
It only goes to show

685
00:36:27,239 --> 00:36:28,280
how he feels about you.

686
00:36:32,239 --> 00:36:33,119
What I believe is this—

687
00:36:33,719 --> 00:36:35,400
rather than waste away here in the Gu household

688
00:36:36,039 --> 00:36:37,960
you'd be better off leaving the Master

689
00:36:38,719 --> 00:36:39,880
and returning to Tongzhou.

690
00:36:40,320 --> 00:36:41,960
We can build a good life on our own.

691
00:36:42,679 --> 00:36:44,119
You wouldn't have to keep using your dowry

692
00:36:44,320 --> 00:36:45,039
to support him.

693
00:36:45,559 --> 00:36:46,440
Let them fend for themselves.

694
00:36:47,400 --> 00:36:48,559
Are you suggesting

695
00:36:49,960 --> 00:36:52,280
that I should divorce your father?

696
00:36:54,920 --> 00:36:55,719
No, no, no.

697
00:36:57,400 --> 00:36:58,239
Let me explain.
Say no more.

698
00:37:01,159 --> 00:37:02,199
this is utterly impossible.

699
00:37:03,760 --> 00:37:04,440
Why?

700
00:37:05,480 --> 00:37:06,559
What are you afraid of?

701
00:37:06,920 --> 00:37:08,440
Your grandmother is old.

702
00:37:09,639 --> 00:37:11,079
She couldn't bear something like this.

703
00:37:11,599 --> 00:37:13,119
Grandmother wouldn't mind.

704
00:37:13,679 --> 00:37:14,960
All her life

705
00:37:15,559 --> 00:37:16,480
what she's cared about most

706
00:37:17,039 --> 00:37:18,159
is that you live well.

707
00:37:19,039 --> 00:37:20,519
And what of you and Jinrong?

708
00:37:22,280 --> 00:37:23,079
The two of you—

709
00:37:23,280 --> 00:37:24,679
one unwed, one unbetrothed.

710
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:25,440
If I

711
00:37:25,440 --> 00:37:27,000
were truly to divorce your father

712
00:37:27,199 --> 00:37:28,320
what would become of the two of you?

713
00:37:28,920 --> 00:37:29,800
Who would be willing to marry

714
00:37:29,800 --> 00:37:31,239
a girl whose mother left her husband?

715
00:37:31,239 --> 00:37:32,159
Take such a girl as a daughter-in-law?

716
00:37:32,960 --> 00:37:33,840
And who would be willing

717
00:37:33,840 --> 00:37:35,320
to marry their fine, respectable daughter

718
00:37:35,559 --> 00:37:37,440
into a household broken by divorce?

719
00:37:38,559 --> 00:37:39,239
No.

720
00:37:39,760 --> 00:37:40,880
It must never happen.

721
00:37:42,079 --> 00:37:43,400
But in this household

722
00:37:43,599 --> 00:37:44,599
you are not happy.

723
00:37:45,000 --> 00:37:46,559
Rong and I see it with our own eyes—

724
00:37:47,719 --> 00:37:49,519
could we possibly

725
00:37:49,920 --> 00:37:50,880
with clear consciences

726
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:51,960
go off and marry while you suffer?

727
00:37:52,679 --> 00:37:53,960
What sort of people would that make us?

728
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:56,000
And Grandmother—

729
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:57,880
that dear old lady—

730
00:37:58,079 --> 00:37:59,320
what worries her most is you.

731
00:38:01,159 --> 00:38:02,880
She gets up in the night, sighing and sighing

732
00:38:03,519 --> 00:38:04,559
unable to rest.

733
00:38:05,440 --> 00:38:06,719
If you agree to a divorce

734
00:38:08,079 --> 00:38:09,800
no one would be happier than she.

735
00:38:15,960 --> 00:38:17,119
To be honest

736
00:38:17,920 --> 00:38:18,920
all I hope

737
00:38:19,079 --> 00:38:20,599
is that you will truly think this over.

738
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:23,199
Before you were with the Master

739
00:38:23,199 --> 00:38:24,239
what kind of life did you live?

740
00:38:24,880 --> 00:38:26,239
What were those days like?

741
00:38:27,440 --> 00:38:28,320
And now—

742
00:38:29,440 --> 00:38:30,920
what kind of life do you live now?

743
00:38:36,039 --> 00:38:37,159
Not another word.

744
00:38:42,639 --> 00:38:43,159
I will not—

745
00:38:43,159 --> 00:38:44,320
divorce your father.

746
00:38:45,719 --> 00:38:47,760
And besides, your father would never agree to it.

747
00:38:48,880 --> 00:38:50,320
Do not bring this up again.

748
00:38:55,639 --> 00:38:56,280
Molan.

749
00:38:56,800 --> 00:38:57,280
Yes, Madam.

750
00:38:57,280 --> 00:38:58,599
Help me to my bed.

751
00:38:58,840 --> 00:38:59,480
I'm weary.
Yes, Madam.

752
00:39:11,400 --> 00:39:12,440
Is Mrs. Gu  gravely ill?

753
00:39:13,079 --> 00:39:13,480
Yes.

754
00:39:14,320 --> 00:39:15,920
While I was looking into the Mu family's proposal

755
00:39:16,320 --> 00:39:17,559
the Gu household servants told me

756
00:39:17,559 --> 00:39:18,480
that a concubine has been causing trouble—

757
00:39:18,800 --> 00:39:19,360
slipping poison
into Madam Gu's regular medicine.

758
00:39:20,800 --> 00:39:22,000
The household is in complete chaos.

759
00:39:22,480 --> 00:39:23,719
I imagine Miss Gu right now

760
00:39:23,719 --> 00:39:24,719
must be at her wits' end.

761
00:39:26,280 --> 00:39:27,360
This Gu Dezhao

762
00:39:27,800 --> 00:39:29,400
lacking in morals, leaving his house in turmoil—

763
00:39:29,400 --> 00:39:30,599
is hardly fit to hold office at all.

764
00:39:31,360 --> 00:39:32,400
Have the culprits been caught?

765
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:33,639
They have.

766
00:39:33,960 --> 00:39:34,960
Once the matter came to light

767
00:39:35,039 --> 00:39:36,079
Miss Gu seized them herself.

768
00:39:36,559 --> 00:39:37,559
She had people to call upon, then.

769
00:39:38,079 --> 00:39:39,159
Ye Xian helped her.

770
00:39:39,400 --> 00:39:40,840
He had the culprits taken to the Marquis's residence for interrogation.

771
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:41,599
Ye Xian.

772
00:39:44,000 --> 00:39:45,199
She turned to Ye Xian for help.

773
00:39:45,880 --> 00:39:46,559
How—

774
00:39:47,039 --> 00:39:48,159
that I do not know, sir.

775
00:39:48,800 --> 00:39:50,239
As for Madam Gu's grave illness—

776
00:39:51,199 --> 00:39:53,239
has a renowned physician been called in to treat her?

777
00:39:53,920 --> 00:39:54,480
Yes.

778
00:39:55,119 --> 00:39:56,480
Ye Xian assisted there as well—

779
00:39:56,679 --> 00:39:57,719
he brought in a divine healer.

780
00:40:02,920 --> 00:40:04,320
Can't handle the brush or the sword

781
00:40:04,559 --> 00:40:05,880
but ever so diligent in matters like these.

782
00:40:07,000 --> 00:40:07,480
Well.

783
00:40:08,000 --> 00:40:08,719
Go

784
00:40:09,039 --> 00:40:10,360
to the residence of Vice Minister Wu of the Ministry of Revenue.

785
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:10,920
Tell him

786
00:40:11,320 --> 00:40:12,519
I will visit him tomorrow.

787
00:40:12,920 --> 00:40:13,280
Yes.

788
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:15,559
Wait.

789
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:17,880
That won't do.

790
00:40:19,239 --> 00:40:21,119
Vice Minister Wu has only recently taken up his post.

791
00:40:21,440 --> 00:40:22,079
Gu Dezhao

792
00:40:22,079 --> 00:40:23,400
is a mere storehouse director—

793
00:40:23,519 --> 00:40:24,199
he likely doesn't even know

794
00:40:24,360 --> 00:40:25,639
what the man looks like.

795
00:40:26,519 --> 00:40:27,960
Better to have the censors impeach him—

796
00:40:27,960 --> 00:40:29,239
cite his corrupt household morals

797
00:40:29,320 --> 00:40:30,239
favoring the concubine over the wife.

798
00:40:31,480 --> 00:40:32,119
That won't do either.

799
00:40:32,920 --> 00:40:33,679
Not that either.

800
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:37,239
It would harm Jinzhao's reputation.

801
00:40:38,079 --> 00:40:39,800
And if word got out and made a stir

802
00:40:40,280 --> 00:40:41,320
it might also be bad

803
00:40:41,320 --> 00:40:42,280
for Mrs. Gu's condition.

804
00:40:44,280 --> 00:40:45,119
I recall—

805
00:40:45,639 --> 00:40:47,360
Assistant Censor-in-chief Gu Deyuan

806
00:40:47,360 --> 00:40:48,440
is Gu Dezhao's elder brother.

807
00:40:50,039 --> 00:40:50,760
Yes.

808
00:40:53,519 --> 00:40:54,800
No—that won't work either.

809
00:40:58,800 --> 00:41:00,000
It's not right. Not right at all.

810
00:41:13,679 --> 00:41:14,360
Here's what we'll do.

811
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:16,079
Come with me to the Gu Manor.

812
00:41:20,880 --> 00:41:21,400
What is it?

813
00:41:23,360 --> 00:41:24,039
Nothing.

814
00:41:24,960 --> 00:41:25,840
Then let's go.

815
00:41:32,320 --> 00:41:33,320
It really is Mr. Chen.

816
00:41:33,480 --> 00:41:33,880
It is.

817
00:41:34,239 --> 00:41:35,679
Chen Yi climbed over the wall to find me.

818
00:41:35,840 --> 00:41:37,039
He said to keep it quiet and not disturb the household.

819
00:41:44,039 --> 00:41:44,639
Miss Gu.

820
00:41:47,280 --> 00:41:48,480
Mr. Chen is waiting for you over there.

821
00:41:49,280 --> 00:41:49,960
Come with me.

822
00:42:23,599 --> 00:42:24,880
Greetings, Mr. Chen.

823
00:42:27,199 --> 00:42:28,119
Rise.

824
00:42:29,920 --> 00:42:30,760
Between us

825
00:42:31,280 --> 00:42:32,239
here's no need for such formalities.

826
00:42:35,480 --> 00:42:36,679
What's happened in your household—

827
00:42:37,639 --> 00:42:38,679
I've heard something of it.

828
00:42:45,039 --> 00:42:46,119
Take this.

829
00:42:47,320 --> 00:42:48,440
What is it?

830
00:42:55,199 --> 00:42:56,159
Among those who serve under me

831
00:42:56,559 --> 00:42:57,239
there are many

832
00:42:57,320 --> 00:42:58,880
who have been at my side for years.

833
00:42:59,599 --> 00:43:00,880
Most of them are quite skilled.

834
00:43:02,679 --> 00:43:04,039
If you ever find yourself in danger again

835
00:43:04,559 --> 00:43:05,960
just blow on this whistle.

836
00:43:38,199 --> 00:43:39,159
The day after tomorrow

837
00:43:40,000 --> 00:43:40,760
at the Dragon Boat Festival

838
00:43:42,119 --> 00:43:43,280
I will be at Baoxiang Temple.

839
00:43:47,440 --> 00:43:48,920
[He treats me so kindly—]

840
00:43:49,199 --> 00:43:50,760
[what does it truly mean?]
